$5 {Is my recommendation, and we'll analyze it in "Position 3" of this Unit.})
(7... Bd6 {This is a positional line. White usually plays 8.Qxc4, but I suggest
} 8. Na3 $5 {[%csl Yc4][%cal Ga3c4] With the idea of capturing on c4 with the
knight. We'll analyze it in "Position 4" of this Unit.}) 8. Bxb4 Ndxb4 9. Nc3
$5 {My recommendation.} ({The main line is} 9. O-O Rb8 10. Nc3 (10. Na3 {
