Qd1 $1 {[%csl Ye2][%cal Ge2e3,Yd1e2] Our queen was not good on a4 anymore. In
the future, we might think about e3-Qe2.} O-O (11... a4 $2 12. Nxa4 $16) (11...
Nd5 12. e4 $5 Nb6 13. d5 $14 {No games, and this is for sure interesting to
play.}) 12. e3 a4 (12... Nd5 13. Nd2 {looks slightly better:} Nb6 (13... Nxc3
