better structure.}) 10. Rd1 Nc5 11. Qf3 Qb6 {Now White is better in 2 ways.}
12. e4 {is similar.} (12. Nc3 {Simple one.} Nxc3 13. Qxc3 $16) 12... Nf6 13. e5
Nd5 14. Nc3 Nxc3 15. Qxc3 $16 *

